sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist
    participant Dashboard as Kubeflow Dashboard
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Webhook as odh-notebook-controller webhook<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+ mTLS
    participant ODHNBC as odh-notebook-controller<br/>Service Account Token
    participant DSPA as Data Science Pipelines API<br/>8888/TCP HTTP
    participant Router as OpenShift Router /<br/>Istio Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant OAuth as OAuth Proxy /<br/>Notebook Service<br/>80/TCP HTTP
    participant OAuthServer as OAuth Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Notebook as Notebook Container<br/>notebook-port/TCP HTTP
    participant Culler as notebook-controller-culler

    Note over User,Notebook: Flow 1: Notebook Creation and Provisioning

    User->>Dashboard: Request new notebook
    Dashboard->>K8sAPI: POST Notebook CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: Validate/Mutate Notebook<br/>mTLS client cert
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Admission response
    K8sAPI-->>Dashboard: Notebook created

    K8sAPI->>ODHNBC: Watch event: Notebook created
    ODHNBC->>K8sAPI: Create resources<br/>Auth: Service Account Token
    ODHNBC->>DSPA: GET pipeline runtime config<br/>Internal HTTP
    DSPA-->>ODHNBC: Pipeline API endpoint + secrets
    ODHNBC->>K8sAPI: Create StatefulSet, Service,<br/>Route, OAuth, NetworkPolicy, RBAC

    Note over User,Notebook: Flow 2: User Access to Notebook

    User->>Router: HTTPS request<br/>443/TCP TLS1.2+
    Router->>OAuth: Forward to OAuth Proxy<br/>80/TCP HTTP
    OAuth->>OAuthServer: Authenticate user<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    OAuthServer-->>OAuth: Auth token
    OAuth->>Notebook: Proxy request<br/>HTTP (authorized session)
    Notebook-->>OAuth: Jupyter response
    OAuth-->>Router: Response
    Router-->>User: HTTPS response

    Note over User,Notebook: Flow 3: Idle Notebook Culling

    Culler->>Notebook: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP (internal)
    Notebook-->>Culler: Activity metrics
    Culler->>K8sAPI: PATCH Notebook (stop)<br/>Auth: Service Account Token
    K8sAPI-->>Culler: Notebook stopped
